<p><span class="anchor" id="p53"></span>بتلا قطعه وفصله عَن غَيره<a href="#p53" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p54"></span><span class="c2">(بتل)</span> بتلا بعد مَا بَين مَنْكِبَيْه فَهُوَ أبتل وَهِي بتلاء <span class="c2">(ج)</span> بتل<a href="#p54" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>